data.name: btnLoadUser.ToolTip
data.value: Allows you to load a custom ini file created by you or the community to the Current Profile [either Manually or using The Witcher 2 Tweaker], Remember that this file has to be in the proper format all the settings should be under a section named [Rendering]

data.name: TextureDownscale.ToolTip
data.value: This Option determines the amount of downscaling applied to textures, higher values result in lower texture quality. Minimal Performance impact, Always keep it Disabled for Maxmum Graphics Quality 1 = Yes 0 = No
